name: The incrementals session 2 on OBJKT#9373
description: @okinmakesart 'The Incrementals' is a series of 30 minutes updates to my 30 minute speed painting. The artwork here is part of the encapsulation of the entire process over time. Taking the speed painting ethos and applying it to small individual sessions.  Credit to LongShotParadox for the idea of the follow up sessions on that work.  The original speed painting is OBJKT#9373
